credits = "THE GREY TITHE — a NoxDev Studio production.

Original world, text & rules: NoxDev (no Fighting Fantasy IP).
Engine: nox_if_engine (ff-2d6 ruleset)  ·  Shell: nox_ui.

REUSED ART (bound by stable ID via the Studio asset manifest):
  Icons — 496 RPG Icons (OpenGameArt, CC0)
  Portraits & monster avatars — RPG Character Portraits / Monster Avatar Icons
  UI frames — Kenney Fantasy UI Borders (CC0)
  Fonts — Cinzel & UncialAntiqua (OFL), MedievalSharp (OFL)
Section illustration plates: labelled veritas-gamebook placeholders,
  drop-in-replaceable from the Studio (Phase 5 art generation)."
